	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">If its a new keyword, type in the keyword in New Keyword field.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Lastly, click on the Submit button to relate to other content which use the same keywords.</td>
